</caption>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1252,2132,589,1223]" pageId="0" pageNumber="106">• Mesic grassland to semi-arid savanna, arid lowland, and mountain desert.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1252,2132,589,1223]" box="[1255,1912,1105,1134]" pageId="0" pageNumber="106">• 1 genus, 7 species, at least 19 extant taxa.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1252,2132,589,1223]" pageId="0" pageNumber="106">• 2 species Critically Endangered, 2 species Endangered, 1 species Vulnerable; 4 subspecies Extinct since 1600.</paragraph>
